        "text": "<p>Based on the stimulus below, answer the following question:\nMr. Limon maintains accounts under the Single Entry System. His information is as follows:\nParticulars | January 1, 2015 (TK) | December 31, 2015 (TK)\nCurrent Assets | 60,000 TK | 80,000 TK\nNon-Current Assets | 25,000 TK | 40,000 TK\nLiabilities | 20,000 TK | 35,000 TK\nDuring the year, he brought in Additional Capital of 10,000 TK and his Drawings for personal needs were 12,000 TK\nQ. What will be the effect on the business due to the increase of 10,000 TK in Additional Capital?\ni. Cash fund will increase by 10,000 TK\nii. Owner's Equity will increase by 10,000 TK\niii. Net Profit will remain unchanged\nWhich one of the following is correct?</p><div class=\"overflow-x-auto my-4\"><table class=\"min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-700 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700\"><tr class=\"bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800\"><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Particulars</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">January 1, 2015 (TK)</th><th class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">December 31, 2015 (TK)</th></tr><tr class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-900\"><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Current Assets</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-right text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">60,000 TK</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-right text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">80,000 TK</td></tr><tr class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-900\"><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Non-Current Assets</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-right text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">25,000 TK</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-right text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">40,000 TK</td></tr><tr class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-900\"><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-left text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">Liabilities</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-right text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">20,000 TK</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2 text-right text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 border-r border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 last:border-r-0\">35,000 TK</td></tr></table></div>",
        "meta": "Chattogram Board - 2017",
