        "id": 1735,
        "text": "<p>Mr. Mashrafe started a business with TK 3,00,000 TK. Year-end: Cash 1,00,000 TK; Van 50,000 TK; Accounts Receivable 70,000 TK; Accounts Payable 1,50,000 TK; Closing Stock 5,00,000 TK; Investment 80,000 TK; Bank Credit. Balance 30,000 TK. What is the Closing Capital?</p>",
