        "id": 1748,
        "text": "<p>Mr. Osim started a business on Jan 1, 2015, with a capital of TK 4,00,000 TK. At the end of the year, his assets and liabilities were: Cash TK 50,000 TK; Debtors TK 3,00,000 TK; Creditors TK 2,00,000 TK; and Accounts Payable TK 2,00,000 TK. What is the amount of profit/loss for 2015?</p>",
