        "correctAnswer": 1,
        "explanation": "<p>Closing Capital = (Cash + Debtors) - (Creditors + Accounts Payable) = (50,000 TK + 3,00,000 TK) - (2,00,000 TK + 2,00,000 TK) = 3,50,000 TK - 4,00,000 TK = (-) 50,000 TK.\n\nProfit/Loss = Closing Capital - Opening Capital = (-50,000 TK) - 4,00,000 TK = (-) 4,50,000 TK (Loss).</p>"
